        %a{:href=>"https://github.com/pauldijou"} my GitHub page.
        I'm mainly working on
        %a{:href=>"https://github.com/richfaces"} RichFaces
        right now and making some translations for
        %a{:href=>"https://github.com/arquillian"} Arquillian
