        About the website
      %p
        The core design is powered with
        %a{:href=>"http://twitter.github.com/bootstrap/index.html"} Twitter Boostrap.
        Thanks to it, this website is fully responsive on any device and has a great look. There is also inspiration from
        %a{:href=>"http://line25.com/"} Line25
        for the title style.
      %p
        The website code is generated by using
        %a{:href=>"http://awestruct.org/"} Awestruct
        which is a real awesome tool. If you want a generator engine for HTML website and you are not afraid by a bit of Ruby code, you need to give it a try! Lots of inspiration from
        %a{:href=>"http://arquillian.org"} Arquillian website
        which is also build using
        %a{:href=>"http://awestruct.org/"} Awestruct
        but with some many hand-made functionnalities.
      %p
        The whole site is hosted at
        %a{:href=>"https://github.com/"} GitHub
        in a
        %a{:href=>"https://github.com/pauldijou/pauldijou.github.com"} Git repo.
        The
        %code master
        branch contains the generated code you are currently seeing in your browser, the
        %code develop
        branch contains the
        %a{:href=>"http://awestruct.org/"} Awestruct
        code in order to generate this code. For more info about hosting a website on
        %a{:href=>"https://github.com/"} GitHub
        , read
        %a{:href=>"http://help.github.com/pages/"} GitHub Pages help.
